# Seed data: the RAW downloads (kaikki extracts, Tatoeba dumps — hundreds of
# MB, cached) stay out of git; the MERGED corpus TSVs the seeders consume ARE
# committed (~25MB total) so setup_db.sh rebuilds the exact same content
# without internet, per the project's reproducibility bar.
data/raw/
# Legacy OpenRussian dumps (host is gone; kept ignored in case of stale copies)
data/ru_words.tsv
data/ru_translations.tsv
node_modules/
